---
title: Smokey Pork Burgers with Aioli & Caramelised Onion
description: These pork burgers have all the flavour of smokey barbeque in a fraction of the time! Don’t be afraid to let the pan get really hot and sizzle as you cook these babies – the more smoke you can see at that point, the more you’ll be tasting later.
